name: Solana broke. Tezos didn't
description:
14/09/2021 Solana is down for 11 hours. Tezos is up and running 24/7/365 for years. No issues, but still 10x less MarketCap from the scam networks that break down or don't even have smart contracts (call me ADA).

This NFT will remind us how long it took Tezos to change places with Solana
